0were%20sourced%20together.%20Every%20step%20became%20a%20shared%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20a%20relative%2C%20Anu%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20your%20job%3F%E2%80%9D%20When%20he%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20a%20senior%20manager%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20grinned%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20my%20own%20business.%20I%E2%80%99m%20the%20CEO.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAryta%20remembers%20the%20stunned%20silence%20that%20followed%2C%20and%20then%20the%20laughter.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20moment%2C%20but%20one%20that%20spoke%20volumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELovebird%20lip%20balms%20%E2%80%94%20infused%20with%20Indian%20fragrances%20and%20vibrant%20colours%20%E2%80%94%20soon%20found%20their%20way%20into%20homes%20and%20even%20corporate%20gifting%20lists.%20Bulk%20orders%20began%20coming%20in.%20Anu%E2%80%99s%20story%20and%20her%20spark%20were%20finding%20their%20way%20into%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20girls%20and%20I%20love%20Anu%E2%80%99s%20lip%20balm.%20We%20had%20the%20honour%20of%20meeting%20her.%20She%20is%20precocious%2C%20confident%2C%20and%20ambitious.%20Everything%20I%20want%20my%20girls%20to%20be%20%E2%80%94%20the%20role%20model%20they%20need.%20She%20is%20the%20embodiment%20of%20girl%20(woman)%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonia%20Singh%2C%20a%20customer%20who%20swears%20by%20Lovebird.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBehind%20the%20brand%3A%20learning%20to%20count%2C%20create%2C%20and%20lead%20with%20heart%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20business%20taught%20Anu%20more%20than%20how%20to%20make%20lip%20balm%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gave%20her%20a%20chance%20to%20build%20life%20skills%20with%20meaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAryta%20broke%20down%20each%20step%20gently%3A%20how%20to%20measure%20ingredients%2C%20why%20hygiene%20mattered%2C%20what%20it%20meant