%93%20The%2023-year-old%20filmmaker%20from%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Shubhika%20Sharma%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20editor%20of%20%E2%80%98Babli%20By%20Night%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyesha%2C%20who%20is%20Neel%E2%80%99s%20maternal%20aunt%2C%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20his%20journey.%20She%20was%20beaming%20with%20pride%20while%20sharing%20how%20she%20felt%20about%20Neel%E2%80%99s%20achievements%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20proud%20of%20him.%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20film%20when%20it%20was%2058%20minutes%20long%20to%20its%20present%20version%20%E2%80%94%20I%20have%20witnessed%20his%20toil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoving%20nature%20is%20one%20thing.%20Turning%20that%20love%20into%20a%20film%20that%20also%20captures%20the%20struggles%20of%20the%20queer%20community%20in%20rural%20India%20%E2%80%94%20that%20takes%20something%20deeper.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20decision%20made%20overnight.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20kind%20of%20work%20that%20grows%20over%20the%20years%2C%20rooted%20in%20a%20quiet%20devotion%20to%20the%20land%20and%20a%20deep%20belief%20in%20the%20stories%20that%20deserve%20to%20be%20seen%20and%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyesha%2C%20who%20practices%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363152%2Fgrow-organic-vegetables-at-home-terrace-garden-homemaker-padma-suresh-income-source%2F%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20herself%20and%20likes%20to%20be%20close%20to%20nature%2C%20candidly%20shares%20one%20of%20her%20fond%20memories%2C%20%E2%80%9CNeel%20and%20I%20started%20going%20to%20the%20forests%20when%20he%20was%20a%20child.%20The%20bond%20that%20we%20share%20today%20is%20because%20of%20wildlife%20and%20nature.%20He%20was%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20old%2C%20and%20we%20were%20at%20our%20farm%20in%20Rajasthan.%20It%20was%20a%20winter%20afternoon%2C%20and%20we%20were%20spending%20time%20in%20the%20greens%20when%20he%20spotted%20a%20bird%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Maasi%2C